</LG>
<LG TYPE="stanza">
<L>The &thorn;rid hour in equal &thorn;at Palomon</L>
<L N="2272">Bigan to Venus temple for to goon</L>
<L>vp roos &thorn;e sonne and vp roos Emelye</L>
<L>And to &thorn;e temple of Dian gan sche hye</L>
<L>Hir maydens &thorn;at sche wi&thorn; hir &thorn;ider ladde</L>
<L N="2276">Ful redily wi&thorn; hem &thorn;e fyr &thorn;ey hadde</L>
<L>Thencens / &thorn;e clo&thorn;es and &thorn;emenant al</L>
<L>That to &thorn;e sacrifice longen schal</L>
<L>The hornes ful of meth as is &thorn;e gyse /</L>
<L N="2280">Ther lakke&thorn; nou&yogh;t to do here sacrifise</L>
<L>Smokyng &thorn;e temple ful of clo&thorn;es faire</L>
<L>This Emelye wi&thorn; herte debonaire</L>
<L>Hir body wessch wi&thorn; wtir of a welle</L>
