<L>Myn be &thorn;e trauail al &thorn;in be &thorn;e glorie</L>
<L>Thy souerein tempul wol I most honouren</L>
<L N="2408">Of any place / and al way most labouren</L>
<L>In &thorn;y plesaunce / and &thorn;y craftes strong</L>
<L>And in &thorn;y tempul I wol my baner hong</L>
<L>And alle &thorn;e armes of my companye</L>
<L N="2412">And euermore vnto &thorn;at day I dye</L>
