<L>And eek to &thorn;is / avow I wol me bynde</L>
<L>My berd myn heer &thorn;at hangeth longe a doun</L>
<L N="2416">That neuer &yogh;it ne felt offensioun</L>
<L>Of rasour ne of schere I wol &thorn;e &yogh;iue</L>
<L>And be &thorn;y trewe seruaunt whiles I lyue</L>
<L>lord haue row&thorn;e vppon my sorwes sore</L>
<L N="2420">&yogh;if me &thorn;y victorie I aske no more</L>
</LG>
<LG TYPE="stanza">
<L>The preyer stynt/ of Arcita &thorn;e strange</L>
<L>The rynges on &thorn;e tempul dore &thorn;at hange</L>
<L>And eek the dores clatereden ful fast</L>
<L N="2424">Of which arcita som what was agast</L>
<L>The fires brenden on &thorn;e auter bright</L>
<L>That it gan al &thorn;e tempul for to light/</L>
<L>A swote smel anon &thorn;e ground vp &yogh;af</L>
<L N="2428">And arcita anon his hand vp haf</L>
<L>And more encens in to &thorn;e fyr &yogh;et cast
<PB REF="00000082.tif" N="70"></L>
<L>with o&thorn;ir rightes and &thorn;an atte last</L>
<L>The statu of mars bigan his hauberk ryng</L>
