<L>I do vengance and pleyn correctioun</L>
<L>whiles I dwelle in &thorn;e signe of &thorn;e lyoun</L>
<L>Myn is &thorn;e ruen of &thorn;e hihe halles</L>
<L N="2464">The fallyng of &thorn;e toures and &thorn;e walles</L>
<L>Vpon &thorn;e mynour or &thorn;e Carpenter
<PB REF="00000083.tif" N="71"></L>
<L>I slowh Sampsoun in schakyng &thorn;e piler</L>
<L>And myne ben &thorn;e maladies colde</L>
<L N="2468">The derke tresoun and &thorn;e castes olde</L>
<L>Myn lokyng is &thorn;e fadir of pestilens</L>
<L>Now wepe nomore I schal do my diligence</L>
<L>That Palomon &thorn;at is myn owen knight</L>
<L N="2472">Schal haue his lady as &thorn;ou him bihight</L>
<L>&thorn;ow marcz schal kepe his kni&yogh;t &yogh;et neuer&thorn;eles</L>
<L>Bitwixe &yogh;ou &thorn;er moot som tyme be pees</L>
<L>Al be &yogh;e nou&yogh;t of oo complexioun<MILESTONE N="33b" UNIT="folio"></L>
<L N="2476">That ilke day cause&thorn; such diuisioun</L>
<L>I am &thorn;i ayel redy at &thorn;y wille</L>
<L>wepe &thorn;ou no more I wol &thorn;i lust fulfille</L>
<L>Now wol I stynt of &thorn;e goddes aboue</L>
<L N="2480">Of mars and of venus goddes of loue</L>
<L>And telle &yogh;ou as pleinly as I can</L>
<L>The grete effecte for &thorn;at I bigan</L>
<L>. . . . .<NOTE PLACE="inter">no gap in the MS.</NOTE></L>
</LG>
<LG TYPE="stanza">
<L>GRet was &thorn;e fest in Athenus &thorn;at day</L>
