<L N="2508">with fyle and hamer prikyng to and fro</L>
<L>&yogh;emen on foote / and knaues many oon</L>
<L>wi&thorn; schorte staues as &thorn;ikke as &thorn;ey may goon</L>
<L>Pypes trompes nakers and Clariounes</L>
<L N="2512">&thorn;at in &thorn;e batail blewe bloody sownes /</L>
<L>The paleys ful of pepul vp and doun<MILESTONE N="34a" UNIT="folio"></L>
<L>heer &thorn;re / &thorn;er / ten / haldyng her questioun</L>
