<L>That same prynce and moeuere eek quod he /</L>
<L>ha&thorn; stabled in &thorn;is wrecched world a doun</L>
<L N="2996">Certeyn dayes and duracioun</L>
<L>To alle &thorn;at er engendrid in &thorn;is place</L>
<L>Ouer &thorn;e day &thorn;ey may nat pace</L>
