<L>Ther wol we first amenden and bygynne /
<PB REF="00000100.tif" N="88"></L>
</LG>
<LG TYPE="stanza">
<L>Sustyr quod he &thorn;is is my ful assent</L>
<L N="3076">wi&thorn; al thauys heer of my parlement</L>
