<L N="1508">wi&thorn; dede bodies . in ful wonder wyse
<PB REF="00000250.tif" N="238"><MILESTONE UNIT="6-text p" N="378"></L>
<L>And speke renably . and as fair and wel</L>
<L>As to &thorn;e Phitonissa dede Samuel</L>
