<L>hayt . brok . hayt . scot . / what spare &yogh;e for &thorn;e stoones</L>
<L N="1544">&THORN;e fend quod he . &yogh;ow fech body and bones
<PB REF="00000251.tif" N="239"><MILESTONE UNIT="6-text p" N="379"></L>
<L>As ferforthly as euer wer &yogh;e folid</L>
