<L>May I nat aske a lybel sir Sompnour</L>
<L N="1596">And answer &thorn;er . by my procuratour</L>
<L>To suche &thorn;ing as . men wol oppose me</L>
<L>&YOGH;is quod &thorn;is sompnour . pay anoon let se</L>
