<L N="1620">Somound vnto &yogh;our court/ in al my lyf</L>
<L>Ne neuer I was but of my body trewe</L>
<L>vnto &thorn;e deuel rough and blak of hiewe</L>
<L>&YOGH;iue I &thorn;y body and &thorn;e panne also</L>
<L N="1624">And whan &thorn;e deuyl herd hir curse so</L>
<L>vpon his knees he sayd in &thorn;is manere</L>
