<DIV2 TYPE="tale"><PB REF="00000488.tif" N="476"><MILESTONE UNIT="6-text p" N="199">
<LG TYPE="stanza">
<L>NO mor of &thorn;is for goddes dignite</L>
<L>Quod our hoste / for &thorn;ou makest me</L>
<L>So wery of &thorn;y verrey lewednesse</L>
<L N="2112">That al so wisly god my soule blesse /</L>
