<L>Now such a rym &thorn;e deuel I byteche</L>
<L>This may wel be rym dogerel quo&thorn; he</L>
<L N="2116">why so quod I why wilt &thorn;ou lette me</L>
<L>More of my tale &thorn;an ano&thorn;er man</L>
<L>Syn &thorn;at it is &thorn;e beste rym &thorn;at I can</L>
<L>By god quod he for pleinly at o word</L>
<L N="2120">&THORN;y drasty rymyng is not worth a tord</L>
<L>&THORN;ou dost nought elles but despendist tyme</L>
<L>Sir at o word &thorn;ou schalt no lenger ryme</L>
<L>let se wher &thorn;ou canst tellen ought in gest</L>
<L N="2124">Or telle in prose som what atte lest<MILESTONE N="206b" UNIT="folio"></L>
<L>In which &thorn;er be so merthe or doctrine</L>
