<L>I wol &yogh;ow telle a litel &thorn;ing in prose</L>
<L N="2128">That oughte like &yogh;ow as I suppose /</L>
<L>Or elles certes &yogh;e be to daungerous</L>
<L>It is a moral tale vertuous</L>
<L>Al be it told som tyme in sondry wise</L>
<L N="2132">Of sondry folk as I schal &yogh;ow deuyse /</L>
<L>As thus. &yogh;e woot &thorn;at euery euaungelist</L>
<L>&THORN;at telle&thorn; vs &thorn;e peyne of Ih&umacr; crist</L>
