<L>As &yogh;e haue herd / &yogh;it to &yogh;ow alle I pray</L>
<L>Blame&thorn; me nought for in my sentence</L>
<L N="2152">Schul &yogh;e no wher fynde difference</L>
<L>Fro &thorn;e sentence of &thorn;is tretys lite</L>
